{{Youmay|the [[Belt/Legends|belt]] known as the GNS strength enhancer|the similar [[strength enhancer]] or the [[CNS strength enhancer|CNS Strength Enhancer]]}}
{{Image}}
The '''GNS strength enhancer''' was a high-powered version of the preexisting, experimental [[CNS strength enhancer]], and was introduced in the period following the [[Jedi Civil War]]. By releasing hormones into the body, the belt-mounted unit increased the performance of muscles, and lacked the protective measures of the CNS unit.

